@startuml REQ-PROD-003_Over-the-Air_Firmware_Update
autonumber
skinparam maxMessageSize 200
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

actor "User" as User
entity "Mobile" as Mobile
entity "Cloud" as Cloud

box "IoT Library" #LightBlue
  participant "OTA Manager" as OTA_Manager
  participant "Comm Manager" as Comm_Manager
end box

header
  **REQ-PROD-003: Over-the-Air Firmware Update**
  //Description:// The system shall support remote firmware updates with\nintegrity verification.
  //Acceptance Criteria:// OTA completes download/flash/verify cycle. Device reports\nsuccess or failure to cloud.
  //Preconditions:// REQ-0020 (Remote Status Reporting)
end header


User -> Mobile: Over-the-Air Firmware Update
activate Mobile
Mobile -> Cloud: Over-the-Air Firmware Update
activate Cloud
Cloud --> OTA_Manager: EVENT_CLOUD_OTA_AVAILABLE
activate OTA_Manager
== OTA_OnUpdateAvailable() ==
note right of OTA_Manager: Ota State Change
OTA_Manager --> Comm_Manager: EVENT_COMM_DOWNLOAD_START
deactivate Cloud
deactivate Mobile
deactivate OTA_Manager

@enduml